{"tid":2178022,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴𢇁打試過鬼剃頭.....","createTime":"2020-08-28T06:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T18:03:07.000Z","uid":50440,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"305a598ca12347e90c750e4f73ed1dcef804cf63","tid":2178022,"uid":50440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:08:51.000Z","msg":"七月初，後尾枕有一個5蚊既size無咗頭髮，去咗睇皮膚科，醫生打咗啲類固醇係頭皮度。點知過咗一星期，其他地方都甩，宜家甩得七七八八了。覆診後醫生話打針無用，要做DPCP。想問下有無巴𢇁打患過呢個病嗎？又會唔會好返呢？"},{"pid":"3ab0a1c532c6070856216e2121026409a56cad07","tid":2178022,"uid":288375,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:13:59.000Z","msg":"我個頭都係有。半年至9個月會生返頭髮。之後又會其他位甩頭髮"},{"pid":"2afc4f4037364eca687c4832a870fd35f5cf4b19","tid":2178022,"uid":144498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:14:51.000Z","msg":"後腦位置有個一蚊銀既窿<br />\n一年後自己生番埋"},{"pid":"5d8da7a485d7b093411fa2e402e673370dd99809","tid":2178022,"uid":13941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:18:01.000Z","msg":"我試過呀 <br />\n轉左洗頭水同查精華就好返好多 <br />\n不過最緊要係你放鬆d唔好諗 <br />\n唔係好難好"},{"pid":"086b504c64ee0e1d2da3c13393199f88288f5970","tid":2178022,"uid":119572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04147f0916fc124ba57718addac2f15353ee7359","tid":2178022,"uid":166591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"086b504c64ee0e1d2da3c13393199f88288f5970","tid":2178022,"uid":119572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:02:42.000Z","msg":"有無辦法唔翻發<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e2819092c5878a17254a7df0b79a67a7cf2c05","tid":2178022,"uid":119572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04147f0916fc124ba57718addac2f15353ee7359","tid":2178022,"uid